description.en: Sometimes, truly focusing on enjoying a meal is no easier than solving math equations. In this series, let's improve focus by overcoming the obstacles that prevent us from staying focused. With the ways back to the state of full concentration, you can feel the power within each moment and the joy within each achievement.

description.en: In face of the uncertainties in life, we may unconsciously feel upset and nervous. Anxiety is like an endless river; the more we against it, the more likely it drowns us. Let go of the chaotic thoughts in your mind. Every single day, take time off to explore the ability to free yourself from anxiety.
